name: Listen to JNZ: Hyperspektiv (audio)
description: This is a single that we (Jungle Noize) released March 9, 2020. The track ('Hyperspektiv'), and the ensuing circumstances of that time, inspired us to take the remainder of the year to work on producing our 4th full length studio album. We wanted to share with the community as we anticipate the official NFT release of our 1 hour LP & its corresponding album art. Enjoy -Jungle Noize
